2--background
-background-color

-background-image:
-url('');note to stop repeating image add
- background-repeat:no-repeat
-background-attachment:fixed,scroll(for image)
-background-position:top,bottom,left,right,then pairings like top left etc(for image)
- background-size:cover(covers entire div),contain(almost similar)
SHORTCUT-background-image:pink url() no repeat fixed centre centre 

3--border:
none,solid,dotted,dashed,double,groove,ridge(light colour),inset,
